6. NFC Functionality
- The app uses react-native-nfc-manager to interact with NFC tags.
- Reviewers can test NFC features using any compatible NFC tag or emulator.
- NFC is used only for reading/writing URLs to tags; no sensitive data is stored on tags.

7. Privacy and Data Handling
- User data is stored securely on the UNQX backend (https://unqx.uz).
- The app does not collect unnecessary personal data.
- Privacy Policy: https://unqx.uz/privacy

8. Compliance Notes
- No in-app purchases or payment UI are present in the iOS version.
- All legal documents (Privacy Policy, Terms of Service) are available on the website.
- The app does not use background location or sensitive device permissions.

